com.inqwell.any.client.swing

Interface InqWindow

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GroupableColumnExample, JDialog, JFrame, JInternalFrame

    public interface InqWindow
    A utility interface that brings together the methods common to JFrame and JInternalFrame for the purposes of simplifying the Inq wrapper structure for these classes.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.4 $
    Author:
    $Author: sanderst $
